Determines, how accurate to draw your actions.
    \n(10) - the smoothest line, can be not very accurate;
    \n(100) - the most accurate line, but can be not very smooth;
    \n(30) - default value.

FP sDraw - 🗒️ is your sheet that is always at hand. A convenient tool that helps in everyday life.
\n
\n✨ Nothing extra - You open it and draw immediately. No ads or intrusive notifications. It has a pleasant and thoughtful design. You can quickly create a sketch, finish a photo, or create a meme.
\n🖋️ The program supports digital pen capabilities: sPen, Smart Pen, Active Pen, etc.
\n⛑️ While you draw, the program periodically creates backup copies to keep your drawing safe.
\n
\n👀 And now more details...
\nAfter opening the program, you don\'t need to spend time creating a project - the sheet is already ready for drawing.
\nThe program is less than a megabyte in size, works stably and quickly on most devices, and does not drain the phone with background activity. Compatible with both current Android versions and Android 2.3 😳
\n
\nWhen drawing, the following options are available:
\n- ↕️ Convenient access to functions using the volume keys;
\n- ⏳ Canceling and repeating actions, for many steps;
\n- 💾 Saving a drawing, several options to choose from;
\n- 📋 Inserting pictures from the gallery or from the clipboard. You can insert after removing the background;
\n- ⚙️ Flexible settings, you can even choose the shape of the buttons 🤩
\n- ❓ There are hints that do not distract, but will help you understand easily.
\n- 🎁 And much more 😉
\n
\nIn addition to simple drawing, there are other tools:
\n- ⬜ Eraser, for erasing what is drawn;
\n- 🏺 Painting to fill the drawn figure;
\n- 🧩 Mosaic to hide something in the photo;
\n- 🅰️ Adding text, with font selection;
\n- ✂️ Selecting and moving a fragment of a picture;
\n- 🔳 Drawing shapes (rectangle, triangle, etc.);
\n- 📏 Ruler, for drawing straight lines;
\n- 🎨 Eyedropper to choose a color from the canvas;
\n- 🖱️ Precision brush, a unique tool that allows you to easily make small changes to your drawing.
\n
